{"tid":478320,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"與少女啪啪才最好？ 清水健萬人斬的他難忘懷阿嬤級女優","createTime":"2017-11-24T03:11:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-26T05:05:03.000Z","uid":37554,"like":174,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":132,"replies":[{"pid":"aaf9f4236613f504636dc051964873e2912147d0","tid":478320,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T03:11:44.000Z","msg":"有「千葉舒馬克」封號的日本知名AV男優清水健，曾經自稱入行20年來，床戰過的AV女優超過1萬人，是名副其實的「萬人斬」。儘管清水健曾和許多知名AV女優交手，仍然無法忘懷與高齡72歲雙胞胎阿嬤啪啪的酥麻感。<br />\n<br />\n清水健最近在推特上PO文表示，看到一則新聞報導，指一名男子無法「無法抗拒15歲少女的靈氣」，犯下性騷擾的罪行，但清水健對這種說法不以為然。清水健說，這種說法太過份了，他以前曾和72歲雙胞胎阿嬤交手過，感覺明明是很酥麻的。<br />\n<br />\n網友回應，認為薑還是老的辣，「敬燕還是很重要的」、「高手中的高手」、「愈老愈猛」、「跟酒一樣愈陳愈香？」。但也有人認為，可能是清水健特殊的性癖好，「叫你阿嬤來啊！」、「我覺得不行」。<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_php58108s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_php58108s.jpg&h=814676d6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d21c59ba8cd66577d32e0d9ce166190475e1ac58","tid":478320,"uid":82394,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T03:14:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好偉大"},{"pid":"612ff08b6e51aa9807a6202bd513aaa7db9a1409","tid":478320,"uid":35592,"like":1328,"dislike":8,"score":1320,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T03:17:10.000Z","msg":"少女唔鋤愛阿婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3840425976657678de81605df1eb2347a216ef88","tid":478320,"uid":1367,"like":14,"dislike":147,"score":-133,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T03:18:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 少女唔鋤愛吖婆..🤮🤮🤮"},{"pid":"04c9d95e7b54535c90048683271f5e4d74a25d59","tid":478320,"uid":32691,"like":4,"dislike":46,"score":-42,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T03:18:10.000Z","msg":"20年 萬人斬<br />\n一日換1.5條女